---
// src/components/About.astro
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      
      <!-- Colonne Gauche : Texte de présentation -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-[#0252b9] uppercase">Who We Are</p>
        <h2 class="mt-2 text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-tight">
          Your Dedicated Partner on the Road
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          At **YAM LOGISTICS LLC**, we believe that truck drivers are the backbone of the economy. That's why we don't just find loads; we build long-term relationships based on transparency, mutual respect, and high profitability.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          Our team of experienced dispatchers works around the clock to negotiate the highest rates on your behalf, plan optimized routes, and handle all the paperwork, so you can focus entirely on driving safely.
        </p>
        
        <!-- Liste de puces esthétiques -->
        <div class="mt-8 space-y-3">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#0252b9] font-bold">✓</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">100% Transparency (No Hidden Fees)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#0252b9] font-bold">✓</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">Top Negotiation to Get You the Highest Rates</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#0252b9] font-bold">✓</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">Dedicated Dispatchers Who Know Your Preferences</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Colonne Droite : Chiffres clés / Stats stylisées -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        
        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 text-center">
          <p class="text-4xl font-black text-[#0252b9]">24/7</p>
          <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400 mt-2">Support</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">Always available for our drivers on the road.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 text-center">
          <p class="text-4xl font-black text-[#0252b9]">0%</p>
          <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400 mt-2">Hassle</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">We manage 100% of the broker paperwork.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 text-center col-span-2">
          <p class="text-4xl font-black text-slate-900">100%</p>
          <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-[#0252b9] mt-2">Dedicated Service</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">We only succeed when our carriers and partners succeed.</p>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>